# Product Showcase Image Generator

When the user asks for a product showcase image, launch image, Twitter thread image, or marketing visual:

1. Use the `generate_image.py` script in this directory
2. Requires: `pip install playwright && playwright install chromium`

## Usage

From URL (auto-screenshot):
```bash
python3 generate_image.py --url https://app.example.com --brand "AppName" -o output.png
```

From screenshot:
```bash
python3 generate_image.py --screenshot app.png --brand "AppName" -o output.png
```

With gradient background:
```bash
python3 generate_image.py --url URL --brand "Name" --gradient "#1a1a2e,#16213e" -o output.png
```

## Options
- `--url` / `--screenshot`: Input (one required)
- `--brand`: Brand name (required)
- `--tagline`: Optional tagline
- `--gradient`: Gradient as "from,to"
- `--tilt`: Rotation degrees (default 4)
- `-o`: Output path (required)
